{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1312,"text":"Michael Browning: engineer,"},{"time":3978,"text":"innovator --"},{"time":5562,"text":"inventor, really --"},{"time":6775,"text":"and inspiring father."},{"time":8594,"text":"He had a passion for flight,\nas you can kind of sense"},{"time":11166,"text":"from that rather dubious\n1970s office-leaving present."},{"time":15691,"text":"And some 40 years after that was created,"},{"time":18526,"text":"a small group of us got together"},{"time":21140,"text":"to have a go,"},{"time":22321,"text":"a run at the whole challenge of flight\nthat inspired people for years,"},{"time":26702,"text":"and do it in a very different kind of way."},{"time":28783,"text":"And that's the journey I'd like\nto share with you now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31492,"text":"The starting hypothesis was one\nof the human mind and body,"},{"time":34734,"text":"which, as you've seen\nfor the last few days here,"},{"time":37152,"text":"is an amazing construct."},{"time":38995,"text":"What if you augmented\nthat wonderful machine"},{"time":42685,"text":"with just the right technology?"},{"time":44187,"text":"If you approach flight\nin that kind of real way,"},{"time":46546,"text":"where could you get to?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":47822,"text":"So my training partner here\nback in London, Denton,"},{"time":51213,"text":"is doing a much better job\nof that kind of stuff than me."},{"time":54241,"text":"Guess what? It's London."},{"time":55925,"text":"The idea was that you augment that."},{"time":58613,"text":"And so, how do you augment that?"},{"time":60191,"text":"Well, we bought one of these."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63216,"text":"This is a micro gas turbine."},{"time":65670,"text":"This was ground zero,"},{"time":67792,"text":"so that little piece of kit\nproved really quite impressive,"},{"time":70965,"text":"so we got two in a field."},{"time":74750,"text":"The real hero here, by the way,\nis, right in the background,"},{"time":77875,"text":"there's a lady tending some vegetables,"},{"time":79808,"text":"who does a brilliant job\nof trying to ignore us for a while --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":82849,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":85829,"text":"I think the only thing\nless happy is the grass,"},{"time":88258,"text":"that we did probably damage quite badly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90734,"text":"You get an idea of the thrust here,"},{"time":92444,"text":"when I try to hold them horizontally\nand somewhat fail."},{"time":95094,"text":"That's around 50 kilos of thrust there."},{"time":97402,"text":"We were quite impressed with that."},{"time":99095,"text":"We thought we were getting somewhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100961,"text":"So there's only one sensible way\nto go from there:"},{"time":104393,"text":"you get four."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105587,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":110798,"text":"I have to say, I still like\nwatching these back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113078,"text":"So then we thought well, let's try\nand spread the load a bit."},{"time":116107,"text":"The legs are designed to take the load,"},{"time":118023,"text":"so why don't we spread it out a bit?"},{"time":120975,"text":"That bit was good."},{"time":123014,"text":"The harness --"},{"time":124421,"text":"a nice idea but it didn't really work,"},{"time":126346,"text":"as you'll see now."},{"time":128112,"text":"This whole journey was very much\nabout trying things --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":130898,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":131996,"text":"Yeah, it really didn't work, did it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":133819,"text":"Trying things and learning\nby failing at them most of the time."},{"time":137595,"text":"And that included failing by falling over."},{"time":142742,"text":"If you notice, we've got\nfive engines here --"},{"time":145051,"text":"not to be put off by the fact\none was in maintenance,"},{"time":147638,"text":"still had a go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148817,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":149848,"text":"And then I pinched a fuel line."},{"time":152535,"text":"So again, good learning.\nWe learned not to do that again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155285,"text":"This was a blind alley."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156509,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":157560,"text":"This was three on each arm --"},{"time":159145,"text":"that was ridiculous."},{"time":160335,"text":"That was 70 kilos on each arm."},{"time":162320,"text":"Again, struck that one off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163937,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":165608,"text":"But we were starting to make\nsome really quite convincing progress,"},{"time":169094,"text":"just enough to make you\nbelieve that maybe --"},{"time":171452,"text":"maybe we could get there."},{"time":173398,"text":"You can see, look -- tantalizing."},{"time":175587,"text":"The model of one on each leg\nand two on each arm,"},{"time":179460,"text":"on paper, that was enough thrust."},{"time":181711,"text":"And then we did what\nI'm about to show you now,"},{"time":184868,"text":"and I still love watching this one."},{"time":189612,"text":"This was our first six-second,\nreasonably coherent flight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195300,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":199983,"text":"That was the point where\nthis endeavor went from:"},{"time":203029,"text":"\"I'm really not sure\nthis is going to work,\""},{"time":205139,"text":"to: \"Oh my god, it does work!\""},{"time":206664,"text":"From there on we then refined it,"},{"time":208283,"text":"but we carried on falling over a lot."},{"time":211093,"text":"Falling over, like I say, is definitely\nthe best way to learn."},{"time":214204,"text":"After a while, we starting\nreally refining the layout of all of this."},{"time":217926,"text":"And you'll see,\nthat's stability and control --"},{"time":220283,"text":"there's no wires there or anything --"},{"time":222137,"text":"that's a combination of us\nrefining the technology,"},{"time":224595,"text":"including with a Tupperware box\non the back for the electronics"},{"time":227822,"text":"and actually learning\nthe balance and control."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232073,"text":"I'm now going to save your ears\nfor the next short piece"},{"time":234750,"text":"and talk over it."},{"time":235933,"text":"After a while, the jet engine\nnoise is a bit annoying."},{"time":238540,"text":"This is only a few weeks ago."},{"time":239966,"text":"You can see the stability and control\nis really quite nice,"},{"time":242915,"text":"and I'd like to think this somewhat\nvalidates that starting hypothesis,"},{"time":246389,"text":"that the human mind and body,\nif properly augmented in that way,"},{"time":251125,"text":"can achieve some pretty cool stuff."},{"time":252935,"text":"I mean, like I said:"},{"time":254532,"text":"I'm not thinking about where\nI'm moving my arms at that stage."},{"time":257520,"text":"I'm looking at the objective\nof where I want to get to,"},{"time":260578,"text":"and a bit like riding a bike,"},{"time":262401,"text":"my arms are just doing their thing."},{"time":264227,"text":"It's a very strange experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265816,"text":"So where is all this headed?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":267516,"text":"I'll talk over this landing --"},{"time":269276,"text":"I think I land in this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271662,"text":"Well, I don't think anybody's going\nto go down to Walmart"},{"time":274610,"text":"or take the kids to school\nin any of this stuff for a while,"},{"time":277519,"text":"but the team at Gravity are building\nsome awesome technology"},{"time":280409,"text":"that's going to make\nthis look like child's play."},{"time":282749,"text":"We're working on some things"},{"time":284122,"text":"that will seek to bring\nthis unusual experience of flight"},{"time":286880,"text":"to a wider audience, beyond the events\nand displays we're doing."},{"time":289946,"text":"We're even starting to look\nfor pilots two and three,"},{"time":292452,"text":"if there's any volunteers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293721,"text":"I've got this vision."},{"time":294943,"text":"It sounds audacious,\nbut let's just stick it out there,"},{"time":297595,"text":"that one day maybe we can\nrise up above a beach,"},{"time":299897,"text":"fly up and down the coastline\nof it, rise up a bit higher,"},{"time":302643,"text":"with some of the safety kit\nwe're working on to make this achievable."},{"time":305935,"text":"Then over the horizon comes\na Hercules with the ramp down."},{"time":308685,"text":"As it comes past,\nyou start picking up speed"},{"time":310774,"text":"and see if we can intercept --"},{"time":312253,"text":"from the rear, not the front,\nthat would be a mistake --"},{"time":314927,"text":"and then try and land in the back."},{"time":316585,"text":"And as I say, that's a little\nway off at the moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319594,"text":"But this is also, if I take\na big step back from this,"},{"time":323538,"text":"this is also a very\npersonal journey for me."},{"time":327352,"text":"Back to that lovely photo,"},{"time":329173,"text":"or photo in a picture."},{"time":331362,"text":"Sadly, my father took\nhis own life when I was 15,"},{"time":334279,"text":"and left an awful lot\nof unfulfilled ambition."},{"time":337271,"text":"He was a wonderful inventor,"},{"time":338919,"text":"a maverick creator."},{"time":340324,"text":"And I'd just like to think,\nif it was possible,"},{"time":343290,"text":"if he was looking down,"},{"time":344630,"text":"he would be --"},{"time":345835,"text":"he'd certainly be smiling at some\nof the things we've done here,"},{"time":348876,"text":"I think."},{"time":350058,"text":"So, it's a tribute to him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351363,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352560,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":356088,"text":"(Voice-over) Richard Browning:\nI'm probably more nervous"},{"time":358795,"text":"about doing the demo after this."},{"time":360357,"text":"I've got a lot of things\nto get done today."},{"time":362401,"text":"Worst-case scenario,\nwe don't get a clean start."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364714,"text":"Or we get an unplanned failure\nwhile I'm actually flying around."},{"time":367958,"text":"This is why we keep it very low,"},{"time":369584,"text":"so the worst is I just look like an idiot\nand fall on my rear, as I said."},{"time":373095,"text":"So you can all enjoy that if that happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375130,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":396174,"text":"(Jet engine accelerates)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":414399,"text":"(Cheers)"}]}]}